      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个图来说明Retail_OrderManagement项目里怎么把main分支的改动合并到未开发分支上。标题就叫'Merge from main onto undeveloped branch'吧。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "title",
