    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，LR横向。'未开发分支'就是develop分支，我们习惯这么叫。流程是：先在main上初始化提交，然后切出develop分支做开发，同时main继续推进，最后把main的新内容合并回develop。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "main",
        "develop",
        "commit",
        "checkout",
        "merge"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，我先画出主干：main分支上先有一个初始commit，然后checkout到develop分支再做一次提交。这样develop就有了自己的开发节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "main",
        "commit",
        "develop",
        "checkout"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，这里需要体现main也在继续推进——得有个checkout main再commit的步骤，不然看不出main有新内容要合并。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "checkout",
        "main",
        "commit"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "加上了，现在图里能看到：develop分支切出去之后，main又往前走了一步。接下来是不是要回到develop做merge？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "checkout",
        "develop",
        "merge",
        "main"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，checkout develop然后merge main，这样就把main的新改动合并到develop分支了。整个流程要清晰展示分支切换和合并点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "checkout",
